    "Our People\nWe are proud to celebrate the remarkable achievements of our faculty members who have been recognised with the SIT and BCD Cluster Teaching and Applied Research Awards, respectively. These accolades underscore the dedication, innovation, and impact of our educators and researchers, who continually strive to advance knowledge, inspire others, and bring about positive societal impact for our learners and industry partners. Their accomplishments are a testament to the high standards and dynamic academic environment that define our institution.\nSIT Teaching Excellence Award (TEA)\nchevron--up\n2024\nAssociate Professor Jawn Lim Tze-hin\nAssistant Professor Nadya Shaznay Patel\nchevron--up\n2023\nAssociate Professor Chu Mui Kim\nAssistant Professor Jesslyn Lim Qian Hui\nAssociate Professor Ng Lee Keng\nchevron--up\n2022\nAssociate Professor Ng Lee Keng\nchevron--up\n2021\nAssociate Professor Chu Mui Kim\nSenior Lecturer Yeap Lay Huay\nchevron--up\n2020\nSenior Lecturer Yeap Lay Huay\nchevron--up\n2019\nAssociate Professor Ng Lee Keng\nchevron--up\n2018\nAssociate Professor Ng Lee Keng\nchevron--up\n2017\nAssociate Professor Ng Lee Keng\nAssociate Professor Jiow Hee Jhee\nchevron--up\n2016\nAssociate Professor Koh Sze Kee\nSIT Applied Research Excellence Award\nchevron--up\n2024\nTeam Award:\nAssociate Professor Agnes Xue Lishan, BCD\nAssociate Professor Desmond Chong, ENG\nAssociate Professor Kwah Li Khim, HSS\nMr Gabriel Kwek, POD\nSIT Fellowship Award\nchevron--up\n2024\nAssociate Professor Chu Mui Kim\nBCD Cluster Excellence in Teaching Award\nchevron--up\n2024\nAssistant Professor Nadya Shaznay Patel\nSenior Lecturer Yeap Lay Huay\nchevron--up\n2023\nAssociate Professor Ng Lee Keng\n(Large Class Teaching)\nAssociate Professor Chu Mui Kim\n(Small Class Teaching)\nAssociate Professor Jawn Lim Tze-hin\n(Teaching Innovation)\nAssociate Professor Jiow Hee Jhee\n(Teaching Supervision)\nchevron--up\n2022\nExemplary Awards:\nAssociate Professor Chu Mui Kim\